\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 1. Product context\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Connect! is a mobile-first PWA that helps people in Doha find pickup sports matches (padel, tennis, football, etc.). Stage 1 is 
\f0\b free player-matching only
\f1\b0  \'97 no payments, no coach/court booking (those are later stages). Audience: young, active players in Doha. Matching is 
\f0\b pull-based
\f1\b0 : hosts post open matches, players self-select in. Can join with or without host approval. 18+ only.\
Stack: Lovable (frontend + basic logic) \uc0\u8594  Supabase (auth + DB) \u8594  GitHub. Heavy logic/refactor handled later in Claude Code.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
