\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 6. Key business logic (the non-obvious rules to tell Lovable)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Pull-based matching:
\f1\b0  players join open matches directly; no host approval.\
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Match status lifecycle:
\f1\b0  open \uc0\u8594  full \u8594  live \u8594  completed \u8594  closed (plus cancelled). The time-based transitions (live / completed / closed) should be 
\f0\b computed from 
\f4\fs26 start_time
\f0\fs24  / 
\f4\fs26 end_time
\f0\fs24  at read time \'97 no cron jobs.
\f1\b0  "completed" = ended, within 24h post-match window. "closed" = 24h passed; recording shuts.\
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Cancellation cutoff:
\f1\b0  anyone (host or player) must cancel \uc0\u8805 3h before start. Cancelling within 3h = a no-show.\
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 No-show = reputation only.
\f1\b0  It's a mark on the player's profile; 
\f0\b no block, no penalty.
\f1\b0  Two sources: (1) within-3h cancellation \uc0\u8594  lands immediately (objective timestamp); (2) "didn't turn up" \u8594  needs corroborating reports to land. Confirming attendance does NOT shield you; host 
\f3\i and
\f1\i0  other players can report.\
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 No-show report threshold (scales with match size):
\f1\b0  2 players \uc0\u8594  1 report \'b7 3\'964 \u8594  2 \'b7 5\'968 \u8594  3 \'b7 9+ \u8594  4 (clamped to number who actually showed). Reports valid 24h after start, one per reporter, participants only. (Full detail in 
\f2\fs26 Connect_NoShow_Spec_1.7.md
\f1\fs24 .)\
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Block:
\f1\b0  tap a username \uc0\u8594  Other-Player Profile \u8594  \u8943  \u8594  Block (stops them seeing you, joining your matches, messaging you).\
\ls8\ilvl0
